{"id":19,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":19,"title":"Chapter 16: King Limhi and His People Escape","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 16"],["h1","King Limhi and His People Escape"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_019_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p3"},"The Lamanites captured many of the Nephites who had not escaped with King Noah. The Lamanites took them away and gave them land but made them pay heavy taxes."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/19.15"},"Mosiah 19:15"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_019_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p5"},"The Nephites made Limhi their new king. Limhi was King Noah’s son, but he was not wicked like his father. He was a good man."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/19.17,26"},"Mosiah 19:17, 26"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_019_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p7"},"King Limhi tried to make peace with the Lamanites, but they continued guarding the Nephites and being cruel to them."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/19.27-28"},"Mosiah 19:27–28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/21.3"},"Mosiah 21:3"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_019_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p9"},"One day King Limhi saw some strangers outside the city. He had them put in prison. The strangers were Nephites from Zarahemla."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/21.23-24"},"Mosiah 21:23–24"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_019_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p11"},"Their leader was named Ammon. King Limhi was happy to see him. He knew that Ammon could help his people escape from the Lamanites."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/7.13-15"},"Mosiah 7:13–15"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_019_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p13"},"King Limhi called his people together. He reminded them that their wickedness was the reason they were being held by the Lamanites."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/7.17,20"},"Mosiah 7:17, 20"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_019_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p15"},"He told his people to repent, trust God, and obey the commandments. Then God would help them escape."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/7.19,33"},"Mosiah 7:19, 33"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_019_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p17"},"The Nephites learned that the Lamanites who guarded the city usually got drunk at night."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/22.6"},"Mosiah 22:6"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.f9"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_019_09.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p19"},"That night King Limhi sent extra wine to the guards as a present."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/22.10"},"Mosiah 22:10"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.f10"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_019_10.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p21"},"King Limhi and his people were able to walk past the drunken guards and escape."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/22.11"},"Mosiah 22:11"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.f11"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_019_11.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p23"},"Ammon guided King Limhi and his people through the wilderness to Zarahemla, where they were welcomed."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-16-king-limhi-and-his-people-escape.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/22.13-14"},"Mosiah 22:13–14"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
